+ * @summary Duplicate class loader deadlock referenced in https://openjdk.org/groups/core-libs/ClassLoaderProposal.html
+ *          One thread loads (A, CL1) extends (B, CL2), while the second loads (C, CL2) extends (D, CL1)
+ * @library /test/lib
